METERED taxi operators are at it again!This time they attacked an Uber car in Hillbrow Joburg.In the video, metered taxi operators armed with knobkerries and other objects can be seen smashing the windows of the Uber car.The driver then tries to get away but got caught up in traffic.Metered taxi operators then followed the Uber car and kept on smashing the windows.Commuters can be seen getting out of the car and running away for safety.